<h2>October 2013</h2>
<p>After the swell of development from DrupalCon, October was also the month with more critical issues fixed than any other month of the 8.x cycle!</p>
<h3>BADCamp</h3>
<p><img src="http://blog.amazeelabs.com/sites/default/files/0-badcamp-4_0.jpg" alt="Numerous sprinters at BADCamp." /><br />
<em>BADCamp pre-sprint<br />
