<h2>December 2013</h2>
<p>We closed 2013 with two big announcements: the <a href="https://drupal.org/node/2135189">New release cycle for core was finalized</a> , as well as the <a href="http://buytaert.net/the-next-step-for-drupal-8-is-a-beta">criteria around Drupal 8 beta 1</a>.</p>
